新球場勢在必行。</p><p><img data-width="990" data-height="928" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/0F/12/rBUC6GUnjyKADiQVAApt4-LmkQk30.jpeg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>]]>
