迪巴拉，3️⃣0️⃣歲生日快樂</p><p><img data-width="1080" data-height="1595" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/16/94/rBUBsmVUlN-AARS5AAFTpL9M6OE89.jpeg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>]]>
